<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l5">auch <expan>vnſ<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> wegen / vvie daʒ dıe Edeln vnd veſten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l6"><expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> cʒu 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Ende </del> End her <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> vnd Peringer </ab>
