<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l9">Hans vnd walther geprüder von Münchweil / den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l10"><expan>B<ex>erhtold</ex></expan> kegler <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>gefange<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd Jm ein pellein mıt kauff = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_166_r1l11">manſchaft <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> heten / darẏnne Jr euch durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
